actually my return to the RP is in the works. I am currently designing 
charachters. Besides if your only reason is to go on the council is to 
promote your own ideas then that is a selfish idea. However my reasons for 
wanting to be on the council is to better the RPG and I have a feeling that 
from talking with them that the coucil understands this. And as for me 
banning you? You arent me so don't say what I will do when you don't know how 
I think. Whenever you get flamed you make comments like that that attract 
them. By all right I have a reason to flame you now but I choose not to. But 
I would also like to point out to the RPG that whenever you make an OOC 
comment almost all contain some derogatory remark about me, which quite 
frankly I am getting sick of.

~Qs7

--part1_129.14183ea6.2a602cd1_boundary
